WEBVTT

00:00:00.158 --> 00:00:02.620
We can all have a bad night of sleep

00:00:02.644 --> 00:00:05.036
and that's perfectly normal,

00:00:05.060 --> 00:00:07.001
but how could we try to improve

00:00:07.025 --> 00:00:10.533
both the quantity
and the quality of our sleep?

00:00:10.950 --> 00:00:13.172
[Sleeping with Science]

00:00:13.196 --> 00:00:15.473
(Music)

00:00:15.497 --> 00:00:19.411
Here are six scientifically grounded tips

00:00:19.435 --> 00:00:20.600
for better sleep.

00:00:20.624 --> 00:00:23.250
The first tip is regularity.

00:00:23.274 --> 00:00:26.646
Go to bed at the same time
and wake up at the same time.

00:00:26.670 --> 00:00:28.765
Regularity is king,

00:00:28.789 --> 00:00:31.272
and it will actually anchor your sleep